Voyager New Moves

Synthesis

Type Category PP Power Accuracy Description
5 0 Restores HP. The amount varies with the weather.

Details

This move restores 1/2 the user's maximum HP in no weather; 2/3 in strong sunlight or solar winds; and 1/4 in rain, hail, or sandstorm.
